Preheat the oven to 180C/356F/Gas 4.For the rose coating, blend all of the ingredients together in a bowl, adding the olive oil last.Season the lamb generously with sea salt and freshly ground black pepper and spread the rose coating all over the skin, using it all up.Place the lamb in the preheated oven for 35 minutes.Remove from the oven and allow to sit for 20 minutes before slicing and serving.